rows.label: bf08280100_0010
rows.name:
Climb up the World Tree to the top?
Very very tiring...

rows.label: bf08280100_0020
rows.name:
It's doesn't look that far from here to
the surface at least.

rows.label: bf08280100_0040
rows.name: Don't you ever quit with that optimism, hmmm?

rows.label: bf08280100_0070
rows.name:
I can see why you've brought Shin, but I advise
you not to let your guard down.

rows.label: bf08280100_0110
rows.name: I don't need your remorse now, Shin.

rows.label: bf08280100_0120
rows.name: But when we're past this crisis, I'm taking you in.

rows.label: bf08280100_0130
rows.name: I owe it to my leader and to my people.

rows.label: bf08280100_0140
rows.name: If you resist, we'll kill you.

rows.label: bf08280100_0180
rows.name:
What? Another monster?
What is it this time?

rows.label: bf08280100_0200
rows.name:
It's the Monoceros!
Are they here for Shin?
